data.description: You will not want to miss this beautiful home located in Mebane. Features include BlackForest hardwood flooring, granite countertops, tile backsplash, custom cabinets, SS appliances, gas stove, and WIC w/wood shelving. Also includes first floor bedrooms, gas log fireplace in family room, privacy fence and walk-in attic. Recently installed high-speed internet (Lumos) throughout neighborhood, community pool, and only minutes from the interstate. Sellers agreeable to a 2/1 rate buydown.
